11:10.420 --> 11:12.695
AND YOU'RE
GONNA WANT TO FIRE ME.

11:12.740 --> 11:14.071
- YOU'RE CRAZY.
YOU'RE FIRED.

11:14.120 --> 11:16.759
NO WAY. THAT IS--THAT IS
THE WHOLE SECOND ACT.

11:16.810 --> 11:17.799
- THINK ABOUT IT.
THINK ABOUT IT.

11:17.840 --> 11:19.944
CUT THE FIRST TWO SCENES,
READ IT,

11:19.980 --> 11:22.392
AND YOU'LL SEE EVERYTHING
YOU NEED IS IN THERE.

11:22.440 --> 11:23.771
- BUT THERE'S--YOU
DON'T HAVE ALL THE INFORMATION.

11:23.820 --> 11:25.321
I'D HAVE TO REWS%R)K THE END OF--

11:25.370 --> 11:27.156
SO?
REWORK IT.

11:27.200 --> 11:28.986
OKAY.
WHAT IS THAT, THREE DAYS?

11:29.030 --> 11:30.167
- NO.
[scoffs]

11:30.200 --> 11:31.758
FOR YOU, MAYBE.

11:31.790 --> 11:32.927
- SARAH...

11:32.960 --> 11:36.373
THERE IS AN OPPORTUNITY
THAT HAS ARISEN

11:36.410 --> 11:41.200
THAT MIGHT GIVE YOU
A STAGED READING

11:41.250 --> 11:43.764
AT THE BERKELEY
TH EATER COMPANY.

11:43.800 --> 11:45.836
- NO.
- YEP.

11:45.870 --> 11:47.110
- [chuckles]
OKAY.

11:47.150 --> 11:49.425
THAT'S REALLY COOL,
BUT IT'S NOT READY.

11:49.460 --> 11:51.769
I SHOULD WAIT UNTIL
IT'S IN BETTER SHAPE.

11:51.810 --> 11:53.846
- YOU COULD DO THESE CHANGES
IN THREE DAYS.

11:53.880 --> 11:56.849
- I COULD IF I DIDN'T
HAVE A FAMILY AND A JOB.

11:56.880 --> 11:59.360
AND IT'S CLOSE, BUT--
- YOU KNOW I CAN'T HELP

11:59.400 --> 12:01.129
BUT THINK
WHAT WOULD HAPPEN

12:01.160 --> 12:03.367
IF YOU PUT ALL THAT
ENERGY YOU HAVE

12:03.410 --> 12:06.470
INTO THIS PLAY.

12:06.510 --> 12:08.330
SARAH...

12:08.380 --> 12:11.099
I HATE TO BE THE ONE
TO TELL YOU.

12:11.140 --> 12:14.200
YOU HAVE A GIFT.
YOU REALLY DO.

12:14.250 --> 12:17.413
THIS IS A GREAT PLAY.
THIS PLAY IS YOU.

12:17.460 --> 12:20.736
FOR ONCE IN YOUR LIFE,
LET YOURSELF COME FIRST.

12:24.810 --> 12:26.778
[doorbell rings]

12:29.050 --> 12:30.290
- HEY.
- HEY.

12:30.330 --> 12:32.059
- YOUR DAD HOME?
- YEAH.

12:36.890 --> 12:38.118
- HEY.
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

12:38.170 --> 12:39.569
WHAT THE HELL DO YOU WANT?

12:39.620 --> 12:42.259
- LOOK, I KNOW YOU'RE
PROBABLY SICK OF ME SAYING IT,

12:42.310 --> 12:44.961
BUT I'M SO SORRY.

12:45.000 --> 12:46.888
AND I HATE
THAT WE'RE NOT TALKING.

12:46.930 --> 12:47.999
- OKAY.
IS THAT IT?

12:48.040 --> 12:50.247
YOU DONE?
- NO, UM...

12:50.280 --> 12:51.963
I WANTED YOU TO KNOW
THAT I'M THINKING ABOUT

12:52.010 --> 12:53.591
BUYING A HOUSE.
- GREAT.

12:53.630 --> 12:55.860
WHAT DO YOU WANT?
YOU WANT TO BORROW SOME MONEY?

12:55.910 --> 12:57.116
BECAUSE YOU CAN'T.
SO YOU CAN GO.

12:57.150 --> 12:59.323
- NO, I DON'T--
I DON'T WANT TO BORROW MONEY.

12:59.360 --> 13:01.942
I KNOW YOU'RE PISSED
AND I TOTALLY UNDERSTAND,

13:01.980 --> 13:03.607
BUT YOU KNOW...

13:03.640 --> 13:04.948
NORMALLY,
YOU WOULD'VE SAID MAYBE,

13:04.990 --> 13:06.946
"THAT'S INTERESTING,
WHY NOW?

13:06.990 --> 13:09.015
YOU DON'T HAVE
A FIANCEE OR A SON ANYMORE."

13:09.060 --> 13:10.607
- MM-HMM.
- TO WHICH I WOULD REPLY,

13:10.650 --> 13:12.925
"THAT'S HOW I'M GONNA
WIN THEM BACK."

13:14.060 --> 13:16.062
- OKAY.
WELL, YOU REALLY ARE AN IDIOT.

13:16.100 --> 13:17.829
- YOU DON'T THINK
IT'S A GOOD IDEA?

13:17.860 --> 13:19.589
- NO, I DON'T.
YOU'RE BEHAVING LIKE A CHILD.

13:19.620 --> 13:21.508
YOU CHEATED ON YOUR FIANCEE,
AND NOW YOU THINK THAT

13:21.550 --> 13:23.552
GOING AND BUYING A HOUSE
IS GONNA MAKE IT ALL BETTER?

13:23.590 --> 13:26.832
I MEAN, SERIOUSLY?
THAT'S YOUR PLAN?

13:26.870 --> 13:29.316
- ACTUALLY, YEAH, THAT'S
THE PLAN AS OF RIGHT NOW.

13:29.360 --> 13:30.839
- WELL, THAT'S
A STUPID PLAN, OKAY?

13:30.870 --> 13:31.802
AND IT'S
FURTHER PROOF TO ME

13:31.840 --> 13:33.569
THAT YOU ARE IMMATURE
AND IRRESPONSIBLE.

13:33.600 --> 13:34.908
- OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT,
I SCREWED UP.

13:34.950 --> 13:35.769
I CHEATED ON MY FIANCEE

13:35.810 --> 13:37.254
AND I RUINED THINGS
HERE FOR YOU.

13:37.290 --> 13:38.496
- YOU SURE DID.
- AND I'M SORRY ABOUT THAT.

13:38.540 --> 13:40.053
BUT THAT DOESN'T
MEAN EVERY SINGLE DECISION

13:40.090 --> 13:42.604
I MAKE NOW IS STUPID
OR IMMATURE, ALL RIGHT?

13:42.640 --> 13:43.743
HAVE YOU EVER NIOADE A MISTAKE?

13:43.780 --> 13:46.169
NO, I HAVEN'T, ACTUALLY.
I NEVER HAVE MADE A MISTAKE.

13:46.200 --> 13:47.883
NOT LIKE THAT,
OKAY?

13:47.930 --> 13:49.306
SO GO BUY YOUR HOUSE
AND MAKE YOUR LIFE ALL BETTER.

13:49.340 --> 13:51.308
- OKAY, I'LL BUY THE HOUSE.
- GOOD, GO BUY IT.

13:51.340 --> 13:52.546
- GREAT.
- OKAY.

13:52.590 --> 13:53.659
- FINE.
- LEAVE ME OUT OF IT.

13:53.690 --> 13:55.237
- YEAH.

13:55.280 --> 13:57.271
THANK YOU.
- YOU'RE WELCOME.

14:06.600 --> 14:07.999
- PERFECT.
- [glggleSJ

